{"tid":2130630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"串連第三波疫情同立法會選舉後 大膽講句根本係政府陰謀","createTime":"2020-07-29T10:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T11:19:57.000Z","uid":199893,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f72e9e3e3892067bf1ccfdb6495dc16afc79bac0","tid":2130630,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"一，引發第三波疫情嘅係政府<br />\n二，政府因第三波疫情打算推後立法會選舉<br />\n三，民意好清晰 大部分港人支持民主陣營<br />\n<br />\n政府好清楚九月如常舉行立法會選舉<br />\n係一定會輸到仆街<br />\n佢地唔想輸立法會咁要點做？<br />\n形象工程同種票囉<br />\n如果九月如常投票 單靠種票冇撚用架<br />\n而且好明顯 一定要揾嘢掩飾<br />\n所以一定要係咁宣傳 扮到有人支持佢地<br />\n<br />\n但形象工程要時間 點樣爭取時間？<br />\n推後選舉囉<br />\n<br />\n點樣推後選舉？<br />\n引爆第三波疫情囉<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇最大得益者根本就係港共<br />\n<br />\n有人可能話：<br />\n<em>唔係喎 而家連好多藍屍都好撚憎政府喎</em><br />\n但呢批人而家憎政府其實對政府冇影響<br />\n港共既然會推後選舉<br />\n而家藍屍一兩個月嘅怒火根本好快就會熄<br />\n一年後咪又係會投返港共<br />\n<br />\n所以港共而家就算激嬲晒啲藍屍 都唔介意"},{"pid":"abf449fe9707ec710114d8693c409ef39cd74469","tid":2130630,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139f5746f1fd60eb5c2fd9b74a0d3decab599bb","tid":2130630,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69220e8352217793a2894b2402e36f0d94cd0255","tid":2130630,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"穿鑿附會"},{"pid":"54b92dc519988d6241291acfee423f93ea677fd0","tid":2130630,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c849999d2779fd3a2ad259d82b6a43a8017840","tid":2130630,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69220e8352217793a2894b2402e36f0d94cd0255","tid":2130630,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"穿鑿附會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"感激善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6134732af4fe3d559345d498f50cf94ba770e42","tid":2130630,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"359e054dfe7d8442e126e78637cc9babb425ec08","tid":2130630,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dcaa2b72838ed7b39e5603b20e88193f339bbb","tid":2130630,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"第一第二波其實都係維持咗一個月就無事<br />\n<br />\n推遲一年嘅理由根本站唔住陣腳"}]}